Class PsStageNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.Agent
      • com.dpsframework.PsNodeAgent
        • com.dpsframework.PsStageNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.dpsframework.core.behaviour.BhConstants, PsConstants, jade.core.TimerListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable

    public class PsStageNode
extends PsNodeAgent
implements PsConstants
    The Test-Environment Agent extend 'Production Systems Node-Agent'.

    This agent permits to open an Node-Agent over graphics screen for analyzing a Node by its name.

    The GUI icons are courtesy of:

    https://icons8.com/web-app/category/all/Business.

    Since:
    2016, update at: 2018-07-15
    Version:
    1.7 (Build.1814)
    Author:
    Francisco J. Aguayo (Leon University / IEEE Power & Energy Systems Society Member)
